{"type":null,"faqId":44562,"title":"手机进水怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>手机进水后，请不要尝试开机或按下关机键。若手机使用的是可拆卸电池，请立即取出电池。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>请擦干手机表面的水渍，然后将手机放置到强力吸水环境（如：活性炭、大米、防潮剂）中 48 小时。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>干燥后尝试开机。如果正常开机后，有部分功能缺失，如键盘灯不亮，或屏幕触摸不灵等，则可能发生硬件故障，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=160056\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果手机进入咖啡、可乐、牛奶、海水等液体，请尽快送至服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"63","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400977000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":152,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"手机,进水","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}